race.comment: SHORTCUT (12) broke the maiden status here at the latest effort and will have taken a stack of confidence from that breakthrough victory. Winning rider Mallyon stays on top and can go back-to-back without surprising. BREEZIN' (3) has hit the top-four in all eight runs this campaign and doesn't know how to put in a poor one. Can get a well-deserved win here. ROMANTIC BUBBLE (4) was a dominant Gold Coast winner when facing the starter for the first time and gets the services of Melbourne Cup-winning hoop Dolan in the stirrups. Looks a definite top-three prospect. READY FOR AIMEE (16) gets the deadly Gollan/Jones combination and will be high on confidence following that last-start win. In the mix. EVERY HEART (10) makes some appeal from the low draw.
